{"word":"Perizzites","slug":"perizzites","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Perizzites</b> One of the seven nations in the land of Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=13&verse=7'>Gen 13:7</a><br/> Territory of, given to Abraham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=15&verse=20'>Gen 15:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=8'>Exo 3:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=23'>Exo 23:23</a><br/> Doomed to destruction<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=20&verse=17'>Deu 20:17</a><br/> Not all destroyed; Israelites marry among<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=3&verse=7'>Jdg 3:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=9&verse=2'>Ezr 9:2</a><br/><a href='S:Canaanites'>Canaanites</a>"}]}